FIGURE4,5LUMOTo do this, it was assumed that were Lumo not available, 
passengers would makethe journey using either another rail service, private car, bus or coach travel. 
For routes where air travel isavailable, this option was also integrated into the baseline model. 
Based on publically available datasets andLumo operational data, the alternative mode share for journeys in the baseline scenario was estimated foreach O/D pair. T

